name: DARKNESS
description:
Hello
My name is Martin, I come from Switzerland and live in Zurich. I've been DJing since around 1988 and am known as DJ MAD B in the field of drum & bass. For a long time I was a member of the DJ collective "Metroploitan Bass Scientists", MBS for short, as well as a resident DJ at MUTE.
When I find time and muse, I produce tracks for myself from time to time and now also for you ;).
Here is another track I would like to share here. Enjoy
